      { question: "How many phases does the WHO Surgical Safety Checklist include?", options: ["1 — Time-out only", "2 — Sign-in and Time-out", "3 — Sign-in, Time-out, and Sign-out", "4 — Sign-in, Time-out, Sign-out, and Debrief"], correctIndex: 2, rationale: "The WHO Surgical Safety Checklist has three phases: Sign-in (before anesthesia induction), Time-out (before surgical incision), and Sign-out (before the patient leaves the operating room)." }
